import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'

const ArtistRegister = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group controlId="artistRegisterName">
        <Form.Label>Nom d'artiste</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Votre nom d'artiste" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group controlId="artistRegisterJob">
        <Form.Label>Métier</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Votre métier dans le spectacle" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Button variant="primary" type="submit">S'inscrire</Button>
    </Form>
  )
}

export default ArtistRegister
